#include<stdio.h>
#define g getchar_unlocked
#define ll long long
inline ll int rd()
{
	ll x=0;
	int sign=1;
	char c;
	while(((c=g())<'0'||c>'9')&&c!='-');
	if(c=='-')
	sign=-1,c=g();
	while(c>='0'&&c<='9')
	x=(x<<3)+(x<<1)+c-48,c=g();
	return sign*x;
}
 
 ll hcf(ll a, ll b)
{
return b == 0 ? a : hcf(b, a % b); 
}
int main()
{
    
    int t;
    for(t=rd();t--;)
    
    {
        int n=rd();
        int i=0;
        ll  gcd=rd();
        for(i=1;i<n;i++)
        {
            ll temp=rd();
            if(gcd>1)
            gcd=hcf(gcd,temp);
        }
        printf("%lld\n",gcd);
 
    }
 
}
